    "bio": "HoangSP is an automation expert with deep experience in using n8n, the open-source workflow automation platform. He regularly creates and shares practical automation templates with the n8n community, helping individuals and businesses save time, boost efficiency, and seamlessly integrate their tools and systems. With a strong systems-thinking approach and a talent for process optimization, HoangSP is a leading figure in Vietnam’s growing automation space.",
